Well endowed Nollywood actress, Nkechi Blessing Sunday has revealed why she has been working round the clock. The cross over actress noted that she’s working tirelessly to earn a living and become wealthy in real life and not just on social media. Nkechi, a popular Nollywood actress, noted that being famous and poor isn’t what she signed up for. “I wanna be successful in real life not rich and famous on Instagram. Hence, the reason I wake up every day and grind harder. Who came help when you are hungry? #unstoppable #ogoagbaye”, she caption a photo uploaded on her Instagram. Though she’s of Igbo descent, the beautiful and curvy mother of one is more known in the Nollywood sub-region, the Yoruba movie industry for her versatility such that she plays just any role given to her and interprets them perfectly.